<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="abcb-glossentry" ?><abcb-glossentry xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_e53cf170-3a1e-49b9-942d-76571f407ccc" outputclass="abcb-glossentry"><glossterm id="_bf941671-62c3-4828-a166-194df81df7d6">Control layer</glossterm><glossdef outputclass="glossdef"><p>Any continuous layer that is installed for one or more of the purposes of air, water, vapour or thermal control, including <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1400_0.5.0.xml#_5a207162-320e-44eb-b264-70d6d38aae74" id="_640e714c-b432-4d86-ac84-3253dccdb3f5" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">pliable building membrane</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1446_24.0.0.xml#_58664f4b-1409-41b5-987a-54aec55ac608" id="_14bc8aa9-78f7-48d9-a356-087ee24ab4ac" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">sarking-type material</xref> but excluding waterproofing membranes or the like complying with AS/NZS 4858. </p></glossdef></abcb-glossentry>